    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_GetUsagePercentageByEnergyType",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to calculate and return the energy usage in BTUs for different energy types (Electricity, Gas, and Steam) for a given scenario, identified by a scenario ID. It excludes Chilled Water (CHW) and Transmission and Distribution (TNC) energy types from the calculation. The procedure uses conversion factors specific to the calendar year to convert energy usage into BTUs."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple steps, including data retrieval, conditional logic, and arithmetic operations. It interacts with multiple tables and uses dynamic data based on the current date, which adds to its complexity."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@sid AS INT",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": This parameter represents the scenario ID for which the energy usage percentages are to be calculated. It is used to filter the data in the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "budget.vwTotalBudget",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " view."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "4. Business Logic and Workflow"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Initialization",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure begins by setting "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "NOCOUNT ON",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " to prevent the message indicating the number of rows affected by a SQL statement from being returned. It declares several variables to store conversion multipliers and the calendar year."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Determine Calendar Year",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure calculates the calendar year by extracting the year from the maximum "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "PublishedBillingPeriod",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " in the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "EC3DB.Published_MonthlyPublishedSummaryData",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table. If this year is greater than the current year, it defaults to the current year."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Retrieve Conversion Factors",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": For each energy type (Electricity, Gas, Steam, and Chilled Water), the procedure retrieves the maximum conversion factor ("
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "MMBtusFactor",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ") for the determined calendar year from the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "EC3DB.Factors_ConversionEquivalentsForBtuAndCO2e",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Calculate BTUs",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure calculates the total energy usage in BTUs for each energy type (excluding TNC and CHW) by:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bulletList",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Summing the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "EnergyUsage",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " from the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "budget.vwTotalBudget",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " view for the given scenario ID."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Multiplying the sum by the respective conversion factor."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Rounding the result and converting it to a "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "bigint",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Return Results",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The results are grouped by "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "EnergyType",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " and returned as a result set."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
